title: Daily Sow & Colbert Report - 2012 Complete
description:
All 2012 episodes of The Daily Show & Colbert Report

Episodes are in their broadcast order

I've labelled them by date - then "DS" for Daily Show & "R" for the Report

Each episode is also labelled with the guests name

All files are in AVI format



This is my first upload so any advice is appreciated

I have the complete DS & R going back to 1999 so will upload them all in time

I am trying to find the Kilborn years of the Daily Show if anyone has them ?

I'd like to complete my collection

We don't get these here in Australia so I download each day...I love them


Hope you enjoy them as much as I do

Jonesy
